| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1699 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ae80ed0b-3613-5f52-9da1-94ae3957e2d8"
